{"tid":1982877,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"關於721 大家經常忽略的一幕","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:11:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"def89f998b41c8610f67ff69a109d1e8c05d2777","tid":1982877,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vqhBGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vqhBGY.png&h=bf653f68&s={SIZE}\" />我相信，世界冇咁多巧合。<br />\n<br />\n追究721元朗恐襲，我地不能不探究背後因由。<br />\n<br />\n7月21日，前線抗爭者第一次係2019年高喊「光復香港，時代革命」，直搗侵蝕香港人權自由幕後黑手既核心 － 西環中聯辦，並將漆彈擲向中共政權既象徵。<br />\n<br />\n相信向中聯辦進發呢一個行動，真正令到呢個政權震怒。因為係612之後，港共黑警事隔超過一個月都未曾再次發射橡膠子彈。包圍警總時候冇，「光復上水、沙田」等示威冇，甚至71攻佔立法會，都冇出現過橡膠子彈，當時既黑警一直都忍住左手。直到721，黑警先第二次發射橡膠子彈 [1]。呢一日，佢地係未有用橙旗警示下，多次從天橋高處，狩獵式槍擊示威者，開左超過30槍。<br />\n<br />\n第二次開槍呢件事，本應係當時輿論焦點，理應全港震怒鞭撻。但偏偏無獨有偶，黑警係上環開槍同時間，就出現大家都熟識不過、更為瘋狂既元朗恐襲。結果，當晚既輿論焦點，以至時至今日，大家都比較少提起，721黑警為左保護中聯辦，不惜係忍手超過一個月後，再破殺戒開槍槍擊香港人。自此以後，開槍正式成為常態。我總係認為，每一件事，有一，未必有二，可能只係單一事件，但有二，就必定會有三。而呢個就係經常被遺忘既721上環既重要性。<br />\n<br />\n而家，我請大家再一次記起，再一次提醒身邊人。721既警黑勾結，絕不止於嗰39分鐘，不止於兩名黑警轉身離開既一幕，更加係有上環黑警同時所開嘅30槍，上環前線抗爭者既每一滴血。<br />\n<br />\n721呢單千古冤案，我地香港人必定追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n[1] 補充：612至721間既多次示威行動中，只有71開左六發海棉彈，並冇橡膠子彈。而721當日，有9發橡膠彈，25發海棉彈。資料來源：<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/128554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F128554&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBid%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=2c8ccb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/128554</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：now新聞 - 721警方上環驅散示威者未有示警橋上開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356458&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBid%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=8c3819e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356458&h=4674889c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356458</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fnostakemedicalstudent%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBid%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=4a737f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"},{"pid":"0770b1250395bbf6dd4625fc1618f8818e8a11ae","tid":1982877,"uid":18771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"154efb7b27b512589fee76269f30338efacb9ec2","tid":1982877,"uid":231331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:57:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f6d73fd713891a943f78650c7ebd1a42ec905ae","tid":1982877,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBid%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=6c4246c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm4FxNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCm4FxNr.jpg&h=15d08911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJWHL7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJWHL7v.jpg&h=a12ee600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZ7ovza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZ7ovza.jpg&h=9d247f94&s={SIZE}\